---
title: Cheesy Beef & Filo Pastry Pie with Tomato & Balsamic Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie-loaded beef base that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a light and flakey filo
pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
